<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Virtual Movie Night Invitation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            margin: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #e74c3c;
        }

        p {
            color: #333333;
        }

        a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            background-color: #e74c3c;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        a:hover {
            background-color: #c0392b;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>Virtual Movie Night Invitation</h1>
        <p>Hey [Your Girlfriend's Name],</p>
        <p>Join me for a special virtual movie night this Valentine's Day!</p>
        <p>I've picked a romantic movie that I think we'll both enjoy, and I can't wait to share this experience with you.</p>
        <p>Let's make it a memorable evening filled with laughter, love, and a great movie!</p>
        <a href="[Link to Virtual Movie]" target="_blank">RSVP and Join the Virtual Movie Night</a>
        <p>Looking forward to our virtual date night!</p>
        <p>With love,</p>
        <p>[Your Name]</p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
